               <msContents>
                  <msItem class="#medica" n="1" xml:id="MS_Add_C_13-item1">
                     <title key="work_13247" type="desc">Medical treatises and recipes</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="it">Italian</textLang>
                     <msItem n="1">
                        <locus>(fol. 1)</locus>
                        <rubric>Inchomincereno dalchune chose...apartenentj a Fisicha coe sechondo Ghaliene ed Pocras et Aristotile ed altri aultorj</rubric>
                        <incipit>Douete sapere che lluomo ainse .v. sensi</incipit>
                        <note>At fol. 61 follow short treatises which may be distinct, on fevers, maladies, diseases of child-birth, etc. An index of on fol. iii verso.</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem n="2">
                        <locus>(fol. 90)</locus>
                        <note>A short treatise on disease, composed in 1464 by '<persName key="person_2800" role="aut">maestro Giovanbatista</persName> [chiamato il medicho della Barba, <hi rend="italic">added in index</hi>] al presente medicho nella chasa e degno spedale di Santa Maria nuova di Firenze, e per la drieto chiamato rabbi Uziel d'Anchona ebreo', made at the request of the rector of the hospital, Iachopo di Piero.</note>
                        <incipit>Cariximi frategli</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem n="3">
                        <locus>(fol. 93v)</locus>
                        <author key="person_86995154">Tommaso del Garbo</author>
                        <title key="work_5685">Consiglio contro a pistolenza</title>
                        <note>Pr. Florence, 1522, etc.; ed. P. Ferrato, Bologna, 1866. Repeated at fol. 113.</note>
                        <incipit>In prima il piu sichuro remedio</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem n="4">
                        <locus>(fol. 98)</locus>
                        <rubric>Le sinonime de <persName key="person_63093658" role="aut">Simone Genouese</persName> miste chon altri autorj</rubric>
                        <note>In alphabetical order.</note>
                        <incipit>Artemisia uel chanaparia, id est matricharia maior</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem n="5">
                        <locus>(fol. 117)</locus>
                        <title key="work_13204" type="desc">Medical recipes</title>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem n="6">
                        <locus>(fol. 122v)</locus>
                        <rubric>La uirtu della acqua arzente ouero acqua vite sechondo maestro <persName key="person_86995154" role="aut">Tommaso del Gharbo</persName> e maestro <persName key="person_308211590" role="aut">Antonio dalla Scharparia</persName> e piu altrj singularj fisicj</rubric>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem n="7">
                        <locus>(fol. 126)</locus>
                        <rubric>Questo fia vno Ricettario buono paraghonato ... chomincato a scriuere questo de x<hi rend="italic">o</hi> di luglo 1488. in martedi ed e di <persName key="person_2801" role="scr">Francesco di lucha de rosso</persName> speziale elquale a iscritto di sua <sic>propia</sic> mano</rubric>
                        <note>Written on blank leaves in a volume that had been more calligraphically wirten by the same scribe.</note>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
